                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-329-defend2373 t18310908-329-punish1692"></join>
               Confined Six Months
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>LAWRANCE - <rs id="t18310908-329-verdict1693" type="verdictDescription">
